;; clj-kondo config for the route-planner ClojureScript core.
;;
;; Bug-catching linters stay at defaults; we relax only stylistic ones that
;; fight this project's conventions, plus one Scittle-specific exception:
;;   - line-length: relaxed 80 -> 100; numeric/math lines are column-aligned.
;;   - docstring-no-summary / missing-docstring: docstrings are multi-line
;;     prose, constants are self-describing.
;;   - namespace-name-mismatch: OFF. planner_core.cljs deliberately carries the
;;     dotted ns orca.planner.core but lives at a flat path because Scittle
;;     loads it by direct <script src=…> URL, not via a classpath.
{:linters {:line-length {:max-line-length 100}
           :docstring-no-summary {:level :off}
           :missing-docstring {:level :off}
           :namespace-name-mismatch {:level :off}}}
